description: Paginated list of custom vocabulary items for a given bot locale's custom vocabulary.

parameters.name: botId
parameters.description: The identifier of the version of the bot associated with this custom vocabulary.

parameters.name: botVersion
parameters.description: The bot version of the bot to the list custom vocabulary request.

parameters.name: localeId
parameters.description: The identifier of the language and locale where this custom vocabulary is used. The string must match one of the supported locales. For more information, see Supported languages (https://docs.aws.amazon.com/lexv2/latest/dg/how-languages.html).

nested_items.name: botId

nested_items.name: itemId
nested_items.description: The unique item identifer for the custom vocabulary item from the custom vocabulary list.

nested_items.name: phrase
